      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      253.37,
      290.02,
      266.33
    ],
    "text": "who is complying with the said law.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      289.13,
      525.09,
      302.09
    ],
    "text": "As per T.M. Prakash v The District Collector W.P. No. 17608 of 2013, M.P. No. 1",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "Calibri-BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      312.89,
      524.85,
      325.85
    ],
    "text": "of 2013 on 27 September 2013, the Hon'ble Judge S. Manikumar has held that",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      336.77,
      525.03,
      349.73
    ],
    "text": "when a statute uses the word 'shall', prima facie it is mandatory, but the Court",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      360.53,
      524.64,
      373.49
    ],
    "text": "may ascertain the real intention of the legislature by carefully attending to the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      384.29,
      244.78,
      397.25
    ],
    "text": "whole scope of the statute.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      420.17,
      525.06,
      433.13
    ],
    "text": "Moreover, in the case of M/s. Sainik Motors v State of Rajasthan AIR 1961 SC",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "Calibri-BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      443.95,
      524.96,
      456.91
    ],
    "text": "1480, Hon'ble Mr. Justice Hidayatullah observed that ordinarily though the word",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      467.71,
      524.65,
      480.67
    ],
    "text": "shall is mandatory, it can be interpreted as directory if the context and intention",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      491.59,
      205.3,
      504.55
    ],
    "text": "otherwise demands.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      527.35,
      525.07,
      540.31
    ],
    "text": "In the case of Lakshmanasami Gounder v C.I.T. Selvamani and others (1992) 1",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "Calibri-BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      551.23,
      524.97,
      564.19
    ],
    "text": "SCC 91, K Ramasamy J laid down the following statement with regards to the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      574.99,
      524.9,
      587.95
    ],
    "text": "mandatory nature of word shall in paragraph 5 as; \"...It is settled law that the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      598.78,
      524.61,
      611.74
    ],
    "text": "word 'shall' be construed in the light of the purpose the Act or Rule that seeks to",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      622.66,
      525.13,
      635.62
    ],
    "text": "serve. It is not an invariable rule that even though the word 'shall' be",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      646.42,
      524.76,
      659.38
    ],
    "text": "ordinarily mandatory but in the context or if the intention is, otherwise, it may",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      670.18,
      524.75,
      683.14
    ],
    "text": "be construed to be directory. The construction ultimately depends upon the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      94.58,
      694.06,
      524.62,
      707.02
    ],
    "text": "provisions itself, keeping in view the intendment of the enactment or of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      728.23,
      327.89,
      756.04
    ],
    "text": "Page 5 of 7",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle",
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      74.64,
      520.3,
      87.6
    ],
    "text": "context in which the word 'shall' has been used and the mischief it seeks to avoid.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      98.42,
      520.26,
      111.38
    ],
    "text": "Where the consequence of failure to comply with any requirement of a provision",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      122.3,
      520.17,
      135.26
    ],
    "text": "is provided by the statute itself, the consequence has to be determined with",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      146.06,
      520.33,
      159.02
    ],
    "text": "reference to the nature of the provision, the purpose of enactment and the effect",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      169.82,
      520.28,
      182.78
    ],
    "text": "of non-compliance thereof. In its absence the consequence has to be determined",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      193.7,
      520.37,
      206.66
    ],
    "text": "with reference to the effect of the non-compliance of the provision of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      217.46,
      520.34,
      230.42
    ],
    "text": "legislature. Mere use of the word 'shall' need not be given that connotation in",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      241.34,
      520.02,
      254.3
    ],
    "text": "each and every case that the provision would be invariably interpreted to",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      265.13,
      242.5,
      278.09
    ],
    "text": "be mandatory or directory.\"",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      300.89,
      520.46,
      313.85
    ],
    "text": "In the case of M.N. Gopalakrishna Panicker v State of Kerala (1991] 1 KLJ 75;",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "Calibri-BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      324.77,
      520.16,
      337.73
    ],
    "text": "[1990] 2 KLT 495, the Counsel, on behalf of the petitioner, referred to a decision",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      348.53,
      510.39,
      361.49
    ],
