    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      408.17,
      520.39,
      421.13
    ],
    "text": "U.S. 26, 35 (1998) the Court was of the view that, \"The mandatory 'shall' ...",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      431.95,
      444.72,
      444.91
    ],
    "text": "normally creates an obligation impervious to judicial discretion.\"",
