    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      539.23,
      399.0,
      552.19
    ],
    "text": "regulations, or directives to express what is mandatory.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      574.99,
      520.08,
      587.95
    ],
    "text": "Therefore, the certification by a Gazetted Officer as with regard to the value of",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
